title: notes
read: read: MB/s; db_mean_* = closest READ@SCK to measured mean per size; NA if no read data
write: write: ms/op; db_mean_* = typ_page_ms * ceil(bytes/256) closest to measured mean; NA if no write data
erase: erase: ms/op; db_mean_* = typ_4K/32K/64K closest to measured mean; NA if no erase data
